name: CanarDos
description:
Multiplayer duck platformer.

Escape from the kitchen with the help of your friend ... OR NOT !

You can also make use the kitchen's traps to eliminate your keyboard friend !

Have fun.

Programmer - Jérémy Valero

2D Artist - Thibault Bousquet

3D Artist - Etienne "Marshall" Saulmé

Game Designer - Thomas "ConkerJak" Gonzalez
